abstract: The lawsuit could lead to changes in the workings of Android smartphones, although it could be settled quickly.
snippet: The lawsuit could lead to changes in the workings of Android smartphones, although it could be settled quickly.
lead_paragraph: The lawsuit that Apple filed on Tuesday against HTC, the mobile handset maker, opens up a lot of questions about the future of Android phones like the Nexus One and the cellphone market in general.

headline.main: What Apple vs. HTC Could Mean

abstract: Billboard is reporting that Apple has started to push back against music labels that have worked out exclusive deals with Amazon in exchange for being featured on the online retailer’s MP3 Daily Deal.
